{
  "slide": 10,
  "duration": 46.66,
  "text": "The Executive Command Center is that single dashboard that gives you visibility of all your key activities on site. So this will include your compliance scores per site. It could well be grouped per client group, grouped per region, whatever you want to do, but with the ability to still drill down right to the individual areas. It gives you your NCR accounts, your trends, your aging severity across the business, trend analysis showing whether sites are improving or in a declining state allows you to take faster decisions and fewer surprises. This is the visibility and accountability that is required.",
